        <section id="appeal">
            <h2>Appeal</h2>
            <p>The appeal of long and sharp toenails lies in their contrast between beauty and danger. Their length and sharpness invoke a sense of both sensuality and threat, making them a powerful tool for those who enjoy dominance, roleplay, and visual intensity in their fetishes.</p>
